This mod (hereinafter “the Mod”) is the copyrighted work of kansatsudango.

[Usage]
The Mod is provided free of charge. Commercial use of the Mod is prohibited.
However, monetization through video platforms or livestreaming services
(e.g., ad revenue or streaming income) is explicitly permitted.

[Redistribution]
Redistribution of the Mod, with or without modification, is prohibited.
If you wish to include the Mod's jar file directly in a Modpack, you must
obtain permission from kansatsudango.
(Modpacks that use external links, such as those on CurseForge, do not require permission.)

[Add-ons and Plugins]
Creation and distribution of add-ons, plugins, or data packs that extend
the Mod's functionality are allowed.
However, such works must not include substantial portions of the Mod's
source code or assets.

[Prohibited Activities]
• Selling the Mod or using it for commercial purposes  
• Redistributing the Mod without permission  
• Excessive reuse of the Mod's assets (textures, models, sounds, etc.)  
• Using the Mod to create content that harasses or defames individuals or groups,  
  or content that is extremely violent or otherwise intended to cause discomfort

[Examples]

Allowed:
• Posting or streaming gameplay videos featuring the Mod  
• Publishing Modpacks on CurseForge using external download links  
• Creating and releasing add-ons or plugins intended for use alongside the Mod  
• Using the Mod's source code for personal study or reference  

Not allowed:
• Redistributing the Mod's jar file, or claiming the Mod as your own  
• Publishing plugins or add-ons that include the Mod’s source code or assets in bulk  
• Reusing the Mod’s textures directly in your own Mod (creating similar original assets is fine)  
• Using the Mod to produce defamatory or targeted harassment content against any individual or group  

[Disclaimer]
The creator assumes no responsibility for any damages resulting from the use
of the Mod. Backward compatibility of the source code is not guaranteed, so
please exercise caution when developing plugins or add-ons.
